ChordPro -- perl version of Chord / Chordii

Features:

* Support for the new ChordPro 5.0 standard
* Native PDF generation
* Unicode support (all input is UTF8)
* Support for external TrueType fonts
* Font kerning (with external TrueType fonts)
* Customizable layout, fonts and sizes
* Customizable backends for ChordPro, LilyPond, LaTeX and PDF
  output

Enhancements w.r.t. Chordii:

* Long chords on short syllables do not overwrite the next chord
